added.description: When Steve starts acting like a spoiled brat during the holidays, Stan takes him to see his incarcerated Grandpa Jack, who tells him the story of how he caught Minstrel Krampus, a legendary demon who punishes naughty children on Christmas. Meanwhile, Hayley gets a job at the airport, but quickly realizes that she might not be cut out for customer service.
